title: Dan
text: I didnt know I needed 50 cans of cold brew... Until I realized i needed 50 cans of KC cold brew coffee.. These days, my workouts start and end with a crisp, refreshing KC beverage; no more 5 o clock feeling, no more pre workout jitters, and no more overpriced Starbucks runs. In short, whatever concoction KILL CLIFF brews up in the lab next, you better believe I will be first in line to place an order.. KC brand Hydrogenated ram's urine meant to stabilize and reinforce gastro-pharyngeal strength and tolerance? Bring it on, I'll drink it chilled, straight from the can, post WOD.
